      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so quiet here. everywhere. i walk into the kitchen and i keep expecting to hear him moving around or the sound of his keys on the counter... but it's just nothing. nothing at all. it feels like i'm just haunting my own house. i don't even know why i bother waking up just to sit in this silence.",
